# FindMyLawyer - Environment Variables Template

Copy this file to `.env` in the respective module folders and update with your credentials.

---

### Root / Main Environment Variables
```env
# General
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=5000

# MongoDB
MONGO_URI=<YOUR_MONGODB_ATLAS_URI>

# Authentication
JWT_SECRET=<YOUR_GENERATE_JWT_SECRET>

# Twilio (OTP Services)
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=<YOUR_TWILIO_SID>
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=<YOUR_TWILIO_TOKEN>
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=<YOUR_TWILIO_PHONE>

# Supabase
SUPABASE_URL=<YOUR_SUPABASE_URL>
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=<YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY>
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=<YOUR_SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY>

# Cloudinary (File Uploads)
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=<YOUR_CLOUD_NAME>
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=<YOUR_API_KEY>
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=<YOUR_API_SECRET>

# Firebase (Frontend/Auth)
FIREBASE_API_KEY=<YOUR_FIREBASE_API_KEY>
FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=<YOUR_FIREBASE_DOMAIN>
FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=<YOUR_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID>
FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=<YOUR_FIREBASE_BUCKET>
FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=<YOUR_FIREBASE_SENDER_ID>
FIREBASE_APP_ID=<YOUR_FIREBASE_APP_ID>
```

### Frontend Specific Variables
*Note: Vite requires variables to be prefixed with `VITE_`*
```env
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=<YOUR_SUPABASE_URL>
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=<YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY>
```

---

> [!WARNING]
> **NEVER** commit your finalized `.env` files to GitHub.
